To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private OnBalanceVolume _obv;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_obv = OBV(symbol);

// In OnData()
if (_obv.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "onbalancevolume", _obv.Current.Value);
}
